Electrochemical performances of LIBs using (a,b) pure CuO, (c,d) CuO/NiO(Ni(NO3)2), (e,f) CuO/NiO(NiSO4) nanowires, and (g,h) NiO(NiSO4) sheets as anode electrodes. Please note that (a,c,e,g) show potentials and capacities of the lithiation/delithiation cycles, while (b,d,f,h) show lithiation/delithiation capacities and coulombic efficiencies for 100 cycles. The insets of (a,c,e,g) show the electrochemical performances of the first lithiation/delithiation cycle.
